{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u6a656c8c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px\">Vue.js 的响应式原理基于 Object.defineProperty 方法，通过这个方法可以拦截对对象属性的访问和修改操作。</span></p><p id=\"uf07d9f85\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px\">Vue 在初始化实例时对 data 对象的属性执行递归遍历，使用 Object.defineProperty 将这些属性全部转为 getter/setter，并收集依赖（即数据变化时能通知到的地方，如视图），以实现数据响应式。</span></p><p id=\"ud11e1e4e\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709211577133-b7c9900c-7fe4-4ee5-808f-b875618768c1.png\" width=\"1200\" id=\"u35fbec9f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uec86b36e\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">注意我们图中有三个关键角色：Watcher、Data、和 Render，它们之间会上演这样的故事：</span></p><p id=\"u191302cf\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Vue 会对传入的 data 做处理：为每一个属性添加 getter 和 setter。在这个过程中，涉及到了 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Object.defineProperty</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> 这个方法。同时每一个 Vue 组件实例，都对应着一个 watcher 实例；</span></p><p id=\"u8cfa9d20\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">这个 watcher 实例仿佛一个跟踪狂，它的目光永远跟随着 data： 由于 render 函数的执行依赖于数据的读取，因此渲染时必定会读取 data 属性进而触发其对应的 getter 方法。getter 方法被调用后，会通知到 watcher，watcher 就会把这些 getter 方法被触发的属性记录为“依赖”——这一过程，就是大家常常听到的“</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">依赖收集</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">”过程。</span></p><p id=\"u4cae904c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">如果 data 发生了更新，也就是说被“写”了，此时对应属性的 setter 方法就会被触发。setter 也会去通知 watcher，告诉它“我改变了”。watcher 拿到消息后，立刻跑去告诉 render：“data 变了，你也给我跟着变！”。由此去触发一个 re-render 的过程、与数据更新相关的组件会重新渲染。</span></p><p id=\"u37d06113\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">以下是 Vue 响应式系统的简化版实现：<br />1. 依赖收集：当渲染函数被首次执行时，会访问响应式数据的 getter，此时收集依赖（即当前组件的渲染Watcher）。<br />2. 依赖更新：当响应式数据变化时（setter 被调用），通知之前收集的依赖进行更新，即重新渲染视图。</span></p><h4 id=\"bFDuS\"><span class=\"ne-text\">简化的代码实现</span></h4><p id=\"u93cf74e4\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"y7DyV\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 简化的依赖类\nclass Dep {\n  constructor() {\n    this.subscribers = new Set();\n  }\n\n  depend() {\n    if (activeUpdate) {\n      this.subscribers.add(activeUpdate);\n    }\n  }\n\n  notify() {\n    this.subscribers.forEach(sub =&gt; sub());\n  }\n}\n\nlet activeUpdate = null;\nfunction autorun(update) {\n  function wrappedUpdate() {\n    activeUpdate = wrappedUpdate;\n    update();\n    activeUpdate = null;\n  }\n  wrappedUpdate();\n}\n\n// 响应式函数\nfunction reactive(obj) {\n  Object.keys(obj).forEach(key =&gt; {\n    let internalValue = obj[key];\n    const dep = new Dep();\n    Object.defineProperty(obj, key, {\n      get() {\n        dep.depend();\n        return internalValue;\n      },\n      set(newVal) {\n        internalValue = newVal;\n        dep.notify();\n      }\n    });\n  });\n  return obj;\n}\n\n// 使用示例\nconst state = reactive({ count: 0 });\n\nautorun(() =&gt; {\n  console.log(state.count);\n});\n\nstate.count++;</code></pre><p id=\"u304efbf2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在这个简化的实现中，Dep 类用于管理依赖，即哪些函数依赖于这个数据。autorun 函数用于首次执行传入的函数，并在执行时注册当前活跃的更新函数。reactive 函数则是将一个普通对象转换为响应式对象，为对象的每个属性设置 getter 和 setter，通过它们来进行依赖收集和触发更新。<br /><br />Vue 2.x 使用的是这种基于 Object.defineProperty 的响应式系统。而 Vue 3.x 引入了 Proxy 作为响应式系统的基础，允许更好的性能和更多语言构造的拦截（如数组索引访问等），但核心原理仍然是依赖收集和触发更新。</span></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u6a656c8c\" id=\"u6a656c8c\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue35f3f6b\" id=\"ue35f3f6b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\">Vue.js 的响应式原理基于 Object.defineProperty 方法，通过这个方法可以拦截对对象属性的访问和修改操作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf07d9f85\" id=\"uf07d9f85\"><span data-lake-id=\"u10e8ec2a\" id=\"u10e8ec2a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\">Vue 在初始化实例时对 data 对象的属性执行递归遍历，使用 Object.defineProperty 将这些属性全部转为 getter/setter，并收集依赖（即数据变化时能通知到的地方，如视图），以实现数据响应式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud11e1e4e\" id=\"ud11e1e4e\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F200222%2F1709211577133-b7c9900c-7fe4-4ee5-808f-b875618768c1.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u04c6d1a9-6cf7-4108-a361-93553319d60%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u83e928f4-dcb3-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A82730%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1200%2C%22originHeight%22%3A750%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22VIRTUALDOMTREE%22%2C%22x%22%3A121%2C%22y%22%3A667%2C%22width%22%3A222%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22UNCTION%22%2C%22x%22%3A171%2C%22y%22%3A203%2C%22width%22%3A126%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RE-RENDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A537%2C%22y%22%3A119%2C%22width%22%3A126%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22COMPONENT%22%2C%22x%22%3A157%2C%22y%22%3A133%2C%22width%22%3A148%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TRIGGER%22%2C%22x%22%3A549%2C%22y%22%3A82%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22'TOUCH%22%2C%22x%22%3A393%2C%22y%22%3A459%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GETTER%22%2C%22x%22%3A658%2C%22y%22%3A540%2C%22width%22%3A95%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WATCHER%22%2C%22x%22%3A838%2C%22y%22%3A167%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ASDEPENDENCY%22%2C%22x%22%3A709%2C%22y%22%3A395%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NOTIFY%22%2C%22x%22%3A1092%2C%22y%22%3A387%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SETTER%22%2C%22x%22%3A660%2C%22y%22%3A603%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RENDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A262%2C%22y%22%3A332%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22COLLECT%22%2C%22x%22%3A739%2C%22y%22%3A364%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RENDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A174%2C%22y%22%3A169%2C%22width%22%3A109%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA%22%2C%22x%22%3A667%2C%22y%22%3A484%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8F%A3%22%2C%22x%22%3A223%2C%22y%22%3A376%2C%22width%22%3A16%2C%22height%22%3A52%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdf9f2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u35fbec9f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uec86b36e\" id=\"uec86b36e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub8ad848f\" id=\"ub8ad848f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">注意我们图中有三个关键角色：Watcher、Data、和 Render，它们之间会上演这样的故事：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u191302cf\" id=\"u191302cf\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u099b4e38\" id=\"u099b4e38\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Vue 会对传入的 data 做处理：为每一个属性添加 getter 和 setter。在这个过程中，涉及到了 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uff706639\" id=\"uff706639\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Object.defineProperty</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf2240d15\" id=\"uf2240d15\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> 这个方法。同时每一个 Vue 组件实例，都对应着一个 watcher 实例；</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8cfa9d20\" id=\"u8cfa9d20\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uddc7891e\" id=\"uddc7891e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">这个 watcher 实例仿佛一个跟踪狂，它的目光永远跟随着 data： 由于 render 函数的执行依赖于数据的读取，因此渲染时必定会读取 data 属性进而触发其对应的 getter 方法。getter 方法被调用后，会通知到 watcher，watcher 就会把这些 getter 方法被触发的属性记录为“依赖”——这一过程，就是大家常常听到的“</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u677233e8\" id=\"u677233e8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">依赖收集</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uea24c80b\" id=\"uea24c80b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">”过程。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4cae904c\" id=\"u4cae904c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2eec8431\" id=\"u2eec8431\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">如果 data 发生了更新，也就是说被“写”了，此时对应属性的 setter 方法就会被触发。setter 也会去通知 watcher，告诉它“我改变了”。watcher 拿到消息后，立刻跑去告诉 render：“data 变了，你也给我跟着变！”。由此去触发一个 re-render 的过程、与数据更新相关的组件会重新渲染。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u37d06113\" id=\"u37d06113\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9000c9b3\" id=\"u9000c9b3\">以下是 Vue 响应式系统的简化版实现：<br />1. 依赖收集：当渲染函数被首次执行时，会访问响应式数据的 getter，此时收集依赖（即当前组件的渲染Watcher）。<br />2. 依赖更新：当响应式数据变化时（setter 被调用），通知之前收集的依赖进行更新，即重新渲染视图。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"bFDuS\" id=\"bFDuS\"><span data-lake-id=\"u73f4f13e\" id=\"u73f4f13e\">简化的代码实现</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u93cf74e4\" id=\"u93cf74e4\"><br></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%B1%BB%5Cnclass%20Dep%20%7B%5Cn%20%20constructor()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20this.subscribers%20%3D%20new%20Set()%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%5Cn%20%20depend()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(activeUpdate)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20this.subscribers.add(activeUpdate)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%5Cn%20%20notify()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20this.subscribers.forEach(sub%20%3D%3E%20sub())%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cnlet%20activeUpdate%20%3D%20null%3B%5Cnfunction%20autorun(update)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20function%20wrappedUpdate()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20activeUpdate%20%3D%20wrappedUpdate%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20update()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20activeUpdate%20%3D%20null%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20wrappedUpdate()%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnfunction%20reactive(obj)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20Object.keys(obj).forEach(key%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20let%20internalValue%20%3D%20obj%5Bkey%5D%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20const%20dep%20%3D%20new%20Dep()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20Object.defineProperty(obj%2C%20key%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20get()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20dep.depend()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20internalValue%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20set(newVal)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20internalValue%20%3D%20newVal%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20dep.notify()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20obj%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%5Cnconst%20state%20%3D%20reactive(%7B%20count%3A%200%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%5Cnautorun(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20console.log(state.count)%3B%5Cn%7D)%3B%5Cn%5Cnstate.count%2B%2B%3B%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22Github%20Light%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22y7DyV%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u304efbf2\" id=\"u304efbf2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6cf87170\" id=\"u6cf87170\">在这个简化的实现中，Dep 类用于管理依赖，即哪些函数依赖于这个数据。autorun 函数用于首次执行传入的函数，并在执行时注册当前活跃的更新函数。reactive 函数则是将一个普通对象转换为响应式对象，为对象的每个属性设置 getter 和 setter，通过它们来进行依赖收集和触发更新。<br /><br />Vue 2.x 使用的是这种基于 Object.defineProperty 的响应式系统。而 Vue 3.x 引入了 Proxy 作为响应式系统的基础，允许更好的性能和更多语言构造的拦截（如数组索引访问等），但核心原理仍然是依赖收集和触发更新。</span></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u6a656c8c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px\">Vue.js 的响应式原理基于 Object.defineProperty 方法，通过这个方法可以拦截对对象属性的访问和修改操作。</span></p><p id=\"uf07d9f85\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px\">Vue 在初始化实例时对 data 对象的属性执行递归遍历，使用 Object.defineProperty 将这些属性全部转为 getter/setter，并收集依赖（即数据变化时能通知到的地方，如视图），以实现数据响应式。</span></p><p id=\"ud11e1e4e\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709211577133-b7c9900c-7fe4-4ee5-808f-b875618768c1.png\" width=\"1200\" id=\"u35fbec9f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uec86b36e\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">注意我们图中有三个关键角色：Watcher、Data、和 Render，它们之间会上演这样的故事：</span></p><p id=\"u191302cf\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Vue 会对传入的 data 做处理：为每一个属性添加 getter 和 setter。在这个过程中，涉及到了 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Object.defineProperty</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> 这个方法。同时每一个 Vue 组件实例，都对应着一个 watcher 实例；</span></p><p id=\"u8cfa9d20\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">这个 watcher 实例仿佛一个跟踪狂，它的目光永远跟随着 data： 由于 render 函数的执行依赖于数据的读取，因此渲染时必定会读取 data 属性进而触发其对应的 getter 方法。getter 方法被调用后，会通知到 watcher，watcher 就会把这些 getter 方法被触发的属性记录为“依赖”——这一过程，就是大家常常听到的“</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">依赖收集</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">”过程。</span></p><p id=\"u4cae904c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">如果 data 发生了更新，也就是说被“写”了，此时对应属性的 setter 方法就会被触发。setter 也会去通知 watcher，告诉它“我改变了”。watcher 拿到消息后，立刻跑去告诉 render：“data 变了，你也给我跟着变！”。由此去触发一个 re-render 的过程、与数据更新相关的组件会重新渲染。</span></p><p id=\"u37d06113\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">以下是 Vue 响应式系统的简化版实现：<br />1. 依赖收集：当渲染函数被首次执行时，会访问响应式数据的 getter，此时收集依赖（即当前组件的渲染Watcher）。<br />2. 依赖更新：当响应式数据变化时（setter 被调用），通知之前收集的依赖进行更新，即重新渲染视图。</span></p><h4 id=\"bFDuS\"><span class=\"ne-text\">简化的代码实现</span></h4><p id=\"u93cf74e4\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"y7DyV\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// 简化的依赖类\nclass Dep {\n  constructor() {\n    this.subscribers = new Set();\n  }\n\n  depend() {\n    if (activeUpdate) {\n      this.subscribers.add(activeUpdate);\n    }\n  }\n\n  notify() {\n    this.subscribers.forEach(sub =&gt; sub());\n  }\n}\n\nlet activeUpdate = null;\nfunction autorun(update) {\n  function wrappedUpdate() {\n    activeUpdate = wrappedUpdate;\n    update();\n    activeUpdate = null;\n  }\n  wrappedUpdate();\n}\n\n// 响应式函数\nfunction reactive(obj) {\n  Object.keys(obj).forEach(key =&gt; {\n    let internalValue = obj[key];\n    const dep = new Dep();\n    Object.defineProperty(obj, key, {\n      get() {\n        dep.depend();\n        return internalValue;\n      },\n      set(newVal) {\n        internalValue = newVal;\n        dep.notify();\n      }\n    });\n  });\n  return obj;\n}\n\n// 使用示例\nconst state = reactive({ count: 0 });\n\nautorun(() =&gt; {\n  console.log(state.count);\n});\n\nstate.count++;</code></pre><p id=\"u304efbf2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在这个简化的实现中，Dep 类用于管理依赖，即哪些函数依赖于这个数据。autorun 函数用于首次执行传入的函数，并在执行时注册当前活跃的更新函数。reactive 函数则是将一个普通对象转换为响应式对象，为对象的每个属性设置 getter 和 setter，通过它们来进行依赖收集和触发更新。<br /><br />Vue 2.x 使用的是这种基于 Object.defineProperty 的响应式系统。而 Vue 3.x 引入了 Proxy 作为响应式系统的基础，允许更好的性能和更多语言构造的拦截（如数组索引访问等），但核心原理仍然是依赖收集和触发更新。</span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u6a656c8c\" id=\"u6a656c8c\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue35f3f6b\" id=\"ue35f3f6b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\">Vue.js 的响应式原理基于 Object.defineProperty 方法，通过这个方法可以拦截对对象属性的访问和修改操作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf07d9f85\" id=\"uf07d9f85\"><span data-lake-id=\"u10e8ec2a\" id=\"u10e8ec2a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\">Vue 在初始化实例时对 data 对象的属性执行递归遍历，使用 Object.defineProperty 将这些属性全部转为 getter/setter，并收集依赖（即数据变化时能通知到的地方，如视图），以实现数据响应式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud11e1e4e\" id=\"ud11e1e4e\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F200222%2F1709211577133-b7c9900c-7fe4-4ee5-808f-b875618768c1.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u04c6d1a9-6cf7-4108-a361-93553319d60%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u83e928f4-dcb3-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A82730%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1200%2C%22originHeight%22%3A750%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22VIRTUALDOMTREE%22%2C%22x%22%3A121%2C%22y%22%3A667%2C%22width%22%3A222%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22UNCTION%22%2C%22x%22%3A171%2C%22y%22%3A203%2C%22width%22%3A126%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RE-RENDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A537%2C%22y%22%3A119%2C%22width%22%3A126%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22COMPONENT%22%2C%22x%22%3A157%2C%22y%22%3A133%2C%22width%22%3A148%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TRIGGER%22%2C%22x%22%3A549%2C%22y%22%3A82%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22'TOUCH%22%2C%22x%22%3A393%2C%22y%22%3A459%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GETTER%22%2C%22x%22%3A658%2C%22y%22%3A540%2C%22width%22%3A95%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WATCHER%22%2C%22x%22%3A838%2C%22y%22%3A167%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ASDEPENDENCY%22%2C%22x%22%3A709%2C%22y%22%3A395%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NOTIFY%22%2C%22x%22%3A1092%2C%22y%22%3A387%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22SETTER%22%2C%22x%22%3A660%2C%22y%22%3A603%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RENDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A262%2C%22y%22%3A332%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22COLLECT%22%2C%22x%22%3A739%2C%22y%22%3A364%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RENDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A174%2C%22y%22%3A169%2C%22width%22%3A109%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA%22%2C%22x%22%3A667%2C%22y%22%3A484%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8F%A3%22%2C%22x%22%3A223%2C%22y%22%3A376%2C%22width%22%3A16%2C%22height%22%3A52%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdf9f2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u35fbec9f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uec86b36e\" id=\"uec86b36e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub8ad848f\" id=\"ub8ad848f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">注意我们图中有三个关键角色：Watcher、Data、和 Render，它们之间会上演这样的故事：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u191302cf\" id=\"u191302cf\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u099b4e38\" id=\"u099b4e38\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Vue 会对传入的 data 做处理：为每一个属性添加 getter 和 setter。在这个过程中，涉及到了 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uff706639\" id=\"uff706639\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Object.defineProperty</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf2240d15\" id=\"uf2240d15\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"> 这个方法。同时每一个 Vue 组件实例，都对应着一个 watcher 实例；</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8cfa9d20\" id=\"u8cfa9d20\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uddc7891e\" id=\"uddc7891e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">这个 watcher 实例仿佛一个跟踪狂，它的目光永远跟随着 data： 由于 render 函数的执行依赖于数据的读取，因此渲染时必定会读取 data 属性进而触发其对应的 getter 方法。getter 方法被调用后，会通知到 watcher，watcher 就会把这些 getter 方法被触发的属性记录为“依赖”——这一过程，就是大家常常听到的“</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u677233e8\" id=\"u677233e8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">依赖收集</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uea24c80b\" id=\"uea24c80b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">”过程。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4cae904c\" id=\"u4cae904c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2eec8431\" id=\"u2eec8431\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">如果 data 发生了更新，也就是说被“写”了，此时对应属性的 setter 方法就会被触发。setter 也会去通知 watcher，告诉它“我改变了”。watcher 拿到消息后，立刻跑去告诉 render：“data 变了，你也给我跟着变！”。由此去触发一个 re-render 的过程、与数据更新相关的组件会重新渲染。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u37d06113\" id=\"u37d06113\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9000c9b3\" id=\"u9000c9b3\">以下是 Vue 响应式系统的简化版实现：<br />1. 依赖收集：当渲染函数被首次执行时，会访问响应式数据的 getter，此时收集依赖（即当前组件的渲染Watcher）。<br />2. 依赖更新：当响应式数据变化时（setter 被调用），通知之前收集的依赖进行更新，即重新渲染视图。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"bFDuS\" id=\"bFDuS\"><span data-lake-id=\"u73f4f13e\" id=\"u73f4f13e\">简化的代码实现</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u93cf74e4\" id=\"u93cf74e4\"><br></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%B1%BB%5Cnclass%20Dep%20%7B%5Cn%20%20constructor()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20this.subscribers%20%3D%20new%20Set()%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%5Cn%20%20depend()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(activeUpdate)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20this.subscribers.add(activeUpdate)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%5Cn%20%20notify()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20this.subscribers.forEach(sub%20%3D%3E%20sub())%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cnlet%20activeUpdate%20%3D%20null%3B%5Cnfunction%20autorun(update)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20function%20wrappedUpdate()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20activeUpdate%20%3D%20wrappedUpdate%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20update()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20activeUpdate%20%3D%20null%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20wrappedUpdate()%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnfunction%20reactive(obj)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20Object.keys(obj).forEach(key%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20let%20internalValue%20%3D%20obj%5Bkey%5D%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20const%20dep%20%3D%20new%20Dep()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20Object.defineProperty(obj%2C%20key%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20get()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20dep.depend()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20internalValue%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20set(newVal)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20internalValue%20%3D%20newVal%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20dep.notify()%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20obj%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%5Cnconst%20state%20%3D%20reactive(%7B%20count%3A%200%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%5Cnautorun(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20console.log(state.count)%3B%5Cn%7D)%3B%5Cn%5Cnstate.count%2B%2B%3B%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22Github%20Light%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22y7DyV%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u304efbf2\" id=\"u304efbf2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6cf87170\" id=\"u6cf87170\">在这个简化的实现中，Dep 类用于管理依赖，即哪些函数依赖于这个数据。autorun 函数用于首次执行传入的函数，并在执行时注册当前活跃的更新函数。reactive 函数则是将一个普通对象转换为响应式对象，为对象的每个属性设置 getter 和 setter，通过它们来进行依赖收集和触发更新。<br /><br />Vue 2.x 使用的是这种基于 Object.defineProperty 的响应式系统。而 Vue 3.x 引入了 Proxy 作为响应式系统的基础，允许更好的性能和更多语言构造的拦截（如数组索引访问等），但核心原理仍然是依赖收集和触发更新。</span></p>","word_count":864,"slug":"kfrm2ponok4s772c","type":"Doc","title":"响应式原理","public":1,"cover":"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709211577133-b7c9900c-7fe4-4ee5-808f-b875618768c1.png","custom_cover":"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709211577133-b7c9900c-7fe4-4ee5-808f-b875618768c1.png","description":"Vue.js 的响应式原理基于 Object.defineProperty 方法，通过这个方法可以拦截对对象属性的访问和修改操作。Vue 在初始化实例时对 data 对象的属性执行递归遍历，使用 Object.defineProperty 将这些属性全部转为 getter/setter，并收集...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"image\":1,\"codeblock\":1}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2024-02-29T12:59:06.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2024-02-29T13:06:32.000Z","first_published_at":"2024-02-29T12:59:44.576Z","content_updated_at":"2024-02-29T13:06:32.000Z","id":160118661},"doc_digest":"H9UrxDnwVZArCz3iC9TjfEdzquo"}